data.description: Single family, one story home, located in Rockledge-Central Brevard Co. Easy access to I-95. Three bedrooms, two bathrooms, one car garage. Large back yard with space for swimming pool, buffer easement between back yards. Indoor laundry room with hook-ups. Sliding doors open up to screened in back patio. Sellers disclosures and survey are attached.
